CONCLUSION

This project demonstrates complete backend development including:

✔ JSON parsing
✔ Database schema design
✔ Business logic implementation
✔ Validation handling
✔ Duplicate prevention
✔ REST API development
✔ Clean layered architecture

The system ensures structured data processing, reliable database storage, and efficient API-based retrieval using a localhost environment.
